data.text: @javachik Yes. I did laugh a couple of times so that was worth it.
@nanaslugdiva Saw it on my birthday and it was the romp I needed it to be.

@sly_wit IMO, there was a lot of story work (character work) they really could have done. it shouldn't be the case that I felt I knew the Oceans 11 characters much better than Oceans 8 (and the cast was fewer!)
@nanaslugdiva True. I liked it a lot but I wish they would have done more with developing the latecomer storyline.
